    printf("\n >> In WARMUP round you will be asked a total of 5 questions to test your");
    printf("\n    general knowledge. You are eligible to play the game if you gain points more than");
    printf("\n    bet money, otherwise you can't proceed further to the Challenge Round.");
    printf("\n    First, Second, Third, Fourth and Fifth questions will give you points which is equal to");
    printf("\n    1, 2, 3, 4 and 5 times the amount of bet money, respectively. Otherwise, you will lose");
    printf("\n    the same amount of money for each wrong answer.");
    printf("\n >> IN CHALLANGE ROUND. You will be asked a total of 10 questions.");
    printf("\n    You have 60 seconds for 10 questions. Each right answer will be awarded 20 percent of points");
    printf("\n    which you are able to gain in WARMUP ROUND and you will lose 10 percent of money for each wrong one.");
    printf("\n    End of the CHALLANGE ROUND you must have points more than you bet in order to proceed further to");
    printf("\n    The Millionaire Round !!!");
    printf("\n >> In the MILLIONAIRE ROUND, you will be asked a total of 5 questions.");
    printf("\n >> >> You will have 3 jokers in the beginning: 50/50, Call a friend, Help from the audience");
    printf("\n >> >> First, Second, Third, Fourth and Fifth questions will give you points which is equal to");
    printf("\n       1, 2, 3, 4 and 5 times the amount of points which you gain.");
    printf("\n >> >> You will be informed in more detail in the beginning of the Millionaire Round");
    printf("\n >> You will be given 4 options and you have to press A, B ,C or D for the");
    printf("\n    right option.");
	printf("\n\n\t*********************BEST OF LUCK*********************************");
	}
